name: Documentation for PUBLIC.GRAFFITI.WALL.
description: This is video documentation of burning the SEED WORDS and PASSWORD for the Tezos wallet of PUBLIC.GRAFFITI.WALL (tz1LK2BFwG3daMKZGR321owX4iAJYLxX88T9) to ensure there is no longer access to the wallet other than to airdrop into it. It is sped up by 4x, because it was surprisingly difficult to burn two pieces of paper in a cup (it took 17 minutes). Regardless, we got’er done.
